{
  "name": ".AM-Auto: Ingest + Brief",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Autonomous morning phases: data collection (Slack, Asana, email) then daily brief + dashboard + calendar blocks. No interaction needed.",
  "when": { "type": "userTriggered" },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "Run the autonomous morning routine.\n\nRead and execute ~/shared/context/protocols/am-auto.md.\n\n## Phase 1: Ingest\nPure data collection — Slack scan, Asana sync, email scan. No writes to organs. Output goes to intake/ and morning snapshot files.\n\n## Phase 3: Brief\nRuns AFTER Phase 1 completes. Produces daily brief, dashboard update, and calendar blocks from Phase 1 output.\n\n## Execution\nUse invokeSubAgent for each phase to isolate context. Pass state between phases via files (intake/, morning snapshot). Report completion of both phases with summary stats."
  }
}
